00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:35,380
Let me put back the c squared for a minute.

92
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:42,300
The energy density is the number of particles per unit volume times the energy of a particle.

93
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:46,200
And it has this big fat c squared in front of it.

94
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,200
It's relative.

95
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,660
The c squared is the speed of light.

