00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:51,800
And it gives a huge magnitude.

97
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:55,900
To the energy of even a very light particle.

98
00:06:55,900 --> 00:07:01,620
A dust grain, because of its mass, a tiny dust grain, has enough energy in it to cause

