100
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:03,620
Okay.

101
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:05,540
If it were annihilated.

102
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:09,200
So the energy density due to the particles is large.

103
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:12,080
On the other hand, the particles are moving slowly.

104
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:13,300
Where does pressure come from?

105
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:17,940
Now first of all, the particles are moving very slowly by comparison with the speed of

106
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:18,940
