00:09:56,460 --> 00:10:00,680
the force on that wall divided by the area.

152
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:05,280
Force per unit area is the thing that's called pressure, or force is equal to pressure times

153
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,680
area.

