00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,640
The gas has done some work.

178
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:55,220
If the gas does work, then the energy in the box must decrease.

179
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:59,540
If something does work, then its energy must decrease.

180
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:08,520
So that means that the change in energy in the box, dE, must be minus the pressure times

181
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:12,100
