00:13:34,260 --> 00:13:35,740
justified yet.

202
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:40,140
But let's plug in our guess for an equation of state that pressure is equal to W times

203
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:40,860
energy density.

204
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:41,860
And that just changes p to minus p.

205
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:42,860
So we have to plug in the equation of state.

206
00:13:42,860 --> 00:13:43,860
And that just changes p to minus p.

207
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:44,860
So we have to plug in the equation of state.

208
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:45,860
And that just changes p to minus p.

209
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:50,300
So now we have a total of 4 minus the number W times the energy density.

