00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:52,720
So we have a total of 4 and we're going to plug in the equation of state.

211
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:58,860
Now take all the terms with dV and put them on one side of the equation, and all the

212
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:01,220
terms with dRho and put them on the other side.

213
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:03,420
There's only one term with dRho.

