00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:10,900
in the room,

576
00:36:10,900 --> 00:36:12,900
all possible directions.

577
00:36:12,900 --> 00:36:15,900
We want to know, on the average,

578
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:19,900
what is the square of the cosine of the angle.

