00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:48,900
the direction of every particle,

590
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:52,900
is characterized by a little unit vector in three dimensions.

591
00:36:52,900 --> 00:36:56,900
The unit vector, let's call it n,

592
00:36:56,900 --> 00:37:01,900
