00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:35,900
nx squared plus nx squared,

602
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:37,900
plus ny squared,

603
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:40,900
plus nz squared,

604
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:45,900
equals one.

605
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:49,900
That's just the fact that this is a unit vector.

606
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:50,900
Now let's average.

