00:38:04,900 --> 00:38:05,900
and nz squared,

614
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:07,900
they're all equivalent.

615
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:10,900
They're just related by rotation.

616
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:12,900
If the gas is isotropic,

617
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:13,900
locally isotropic,

618
00:38:13,900 --> 00:38:18,900
so that the velocity distribution is the same in every direction,

