00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:23,900
let's average it,

621
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:26,900
bracket just means average,

622
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:29,900
of nx squared plus ny squared plus nz squared

623
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:31,900
is just one.

