00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:48,900
So what have we found?

635
00:38:48,900 --> 00:38:52,900
We found that the average of the cosine squared of theta

636
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:55,900
is equal to one third.

637
00:38:55,900 --> 00:39:01,900
Pressure equals one third rho.

